  <p><anchor n="T.50.2062.0920a03"/><lb ed="T" n="0920a03"/><persName key="A001336">釋善悟</persName>號<persName key="A001336">高菴</persName>。<placeName key="PL000000043928">洋州</placeName>李氏子。<date key="j21169892117354" from-iso="1084-01-07" to-iso="1085-01-06">年十一</date>得度。生<lb ed="T" n="0920a04"/>有夙慧靈根自發。聞<persName key="A008457">冲禪師</persName>舉<persName key="A002098">梁武帝</persName>問<lb ed="T" n="0920a05"/><persName key="A001361">達磨</persName>因緣。如獲舊物遽曰。<persName key="A001336">我</persName>既廓然。何聖<lb ed="T" n="0920a06"/>之有<persName key="A008457">冲</persName>異<persName key="A001336">其</persName>語勉<persName key="A001336">之</persName>南詢。遂謁<placeName key="PL000000015502">龍門</placeName><persName key="A008397">佛眼</persName>。<lb ed="T" n="0920a07"/>一日有僧被蛇咬。<persName key="A008397">佛眼</persName>問眾曰。既是龍門<lb ed="T" n="0920a08"/>為甚却被蛇咬。<persName key="A001336">悟</persName>應聲曰。果然現大人相。<lb ed="T" n="0920a09"/><persName key="A008397">眼</persName>器<persName key="A001336">之</persName>。後傳此語至<persName key="A001411">佛果</persName>。<persName key="A001411">果</persName>曰。<placeName key="PL000000015502">龍門</placeName>有此<lb ed="T" n="0920a10"/>僧。東山法道未寂寥。爾上堂心生種種法生。<lb ed="T" n="0920a11"/>森羅萬象縱橫信手拈來。便用日輪午後三<lb ed="T" n="0920a12"/>更。心滅種種法滅。四句百非路絕。直饒<persName key="A001361">達磨</persName><lb ed="T" n="0920a13"/>出頭也是眼中金屑。心生心滅是誰木人。携<lb ed="T" n="0920a14"/>手同歸。歸到故鄉田地猶遭頂上一鎚。</p>
